ass="_ _3"></span>安住于远离四边八戏的空性中，<span class="_ _7"></span>这叫做</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y134 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">三轮体空。 </div><div class="t m0 x22 h4 y135 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">当然，<span class="_ _5"></span>也有人连想获得善报的概念都没有，<span class="_ _5"></span>只是随顺别</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
